citRespParty.rpOrgName: Rock County Real Property Description Department

dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data represents addresses for Rock County, Wisconsin in 2019.[The address point feature class was created to assist 911 dispatchers/calltakers in locating wireless E911 callers. Sources include: current aerial photography, NAIP aerial mosaic imagery, parcel maps, limited GPS collection and physical verification when necessary.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This data is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[A current, uniform address point dataset that includes all cities, towns and villages within Rock County is needed to identify addressed structures, which includes but is not limited to: residences, businesses, parks, landmarks, cemeteries, technology structures. This dataset is to be used only as a resource since GPS data collection for every address point is not feasible. This data file is updated as necessary.]

Rock County Land Records Committee
